      • NY Post: Jeff Metcalf interview (Austin Metcalf's father)<br/>
      • WFAA: Hunter Metcalf interview<br/>
      • ABC7 Chicago: Arrest report details, April 5, 2025<br/>
      • Fox4 News: Comprehensive case tracker<br/>
